IOLA Tracking Internal — Full PRD and Context
What this is
A lightweight internal operations platform for Ikirere Orbital Labs Africa (IOLA), a deep tech space startup building satellite coordination software and multipurpose CubeSats for Africa. The platform replaces manual spreadsheets and WhatsApp coordination with a clean, shared workspace where the team tracks fundraising applications, outreach contacts, research progress, and action items — all in one place.
Tech stack

Frontend: React, hosted on Vercel
Database: Supabase (free tier, Postgres under the hood)
Auth: Supabase Auth (email + password, with admin invite flow)
AI assistant: Anthropic Claude API (claude-sonnet-4-20250514) for natural language edits and queries
Styling: Tailwind CSS


Team accounts (5 users)
